  "prompt": "What are the coolest IT companies in Chandigarh, India?",
  "response": "Chandigarh has emerged as a growing hub for IT and tech companies, thanks to its strategic location, quality of life, and educational institutions. Here are some notable IT companies and startups in Chandigarh that are considered cool or innovative:\n\n1. **Tech Mahindra**: Part of the Mahindra Group, this IT services company has a significant presence in Chandigarh, focusing on digital transformation and technology solutions.\n\n2. **Nettlinx**: Specializes in providing IT services, smart city solutions, and cloud-based services. They have a strong emphasis on innovation and technology.\n\n3. **Chandigarh Group of Colleges (CGC) - Innovation Lab**: While not a traditional IT company, CGC has an innovation lab that fosters startups and tech initiatives, making it a hub for new ideas.\n\n4. **Cybrom**: A tech startup focusing on mobile app development, web solutions, and digital marketing, known for its creative approach and innovative projects.\n\n5. **Invoay**: A company that offers IT services, including software development and digital marketing, with a reputation for fostering a creative and collaborative work environment.\n\n6. **Saviom**: An international company with a local presence, Saviom specializes in resource management and project scheduling software, and it has a vibrant workplace culture.\n\n7. **eZee Technosys**: This company provides hospitality management solutions and has a global client base, offering innovative software solutions for the hospitality industry.\n\n8. **Wiz Khalifa**: A digital marketing and web development company that focuses on providing creative and custom solutions for businesses.\n\n9. **Fusion Informatics**: They specialize in mobile app development and enterprise solutions, with a reputation for their innovative approach to technology.\n\n10. **Think360**: A digital marketing agency that provides comprehensive online marketing solutions, known for its innovative campaigns and strategies.\n\nThese companies contribute to the dynamic IT landscape of Chandigarh and are known for their innovative approaches, work culture, and contributions to technology.",
